qas.question: What is the method to demonstrate that no contradictions were created by the addition of axiom of foundation?
Zermelo and Fraenkel's axiom of foundation established that every set be constructed how?

answers.text: from the bottom up in an ordered succession of steps

qas.question: What excluded a set from belonging to itself in set theory?

answers.text: if one set belongs to another then the first must necessarily come before the second in the succession
